tasks.instruction: Generate synthetic training data for carbon stock estimation model with NDVI, canopy cover, soil carbon data, and corresponding carbon sequestration values
Perform exploratory data analysis on the carbon stock dataset to understand data distributions, correlations, and patterns
Implement feature engineering and data preprocessing pipeline for the carbon stock model
Train and compare multiple machine learning models (Random Forest, Gradient Boosting, Neural Network) for carbon sequestration prediction
Evaluate model performance using various metrics and create comprehensive evaluation report with visualizations
